title: add message file to node
body:
This PR is a first part for adding message when cordon/uncordon/drain a node for kubernetes. For more info please take a look at [Kubernetes #55527](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/55527).

title: doc: Clarifying state of the API schema
body:
Previously this README.md stated that in the future, this repo would
contain the schema for the API server.  At this point it squarely does
and is regularly receiving protobuf generated defitions which are
critical to many Kubernetes components.

Sorry, we do not accept changes directly against this repository. Please see 
CONTRIBUTING.md for information on where and how to contribute instead.
